<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Raizefund!</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 40px 0;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table width="480" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px;">
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
                <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Raizefund</h1>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 32px 40px; color: #000000;">
                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Hello {{firstName}},</p>

                <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                  Welcome to <strong>Raizefund</strong> — we’re thrilled to have you join our community of dreamers, builders, and supporters.
                </p>

                <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                  At Raizefund, we believe every idea deserves a chance to grow. Whether you’re here to raise funds, back a cause, or explore new opportunities, you’re now part of something meaningful.
                </p>

                <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 28px;">
                  You can log in anytime to start your journey and discover inspiring projects waiting for your support.
                </p>

                <div style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
                  <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid #000000; color: #000000; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 14px;">
                    Go to Dashboard
                  </a>
                </div>

                <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #333333; margin-bottom: 0;">
                  With warm regards,<br />
                  <strong>The Raizefund Team</strong>
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 14px 0; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666666; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
                © {{year}} Raizefund. All rights reserved.
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
